6525 West Campus Oval is a 2-story, Class A office property located in New Albany, Ohio. Consisting of approximately 68,000 square feet, this building is surrounded by a diverse mix of retail, office and high-end residential. Located just 5 miles from Outerbelt I-270 and 13 miles from John Glenn International Airport, 6525 West Campus Oval serves a prime location.
